[Certainly, the outbreak in 2002-3 was quite large. It also started in backyard flocks and moved into commercial flocks. Hopefully this commercial flock will be contained quickly and will not spread to other flocks. We would like to see this disease in commercial an backyard flocks contained sooner rather than later. - Mod.TG

